title: Citi Field gave Chase Utley a predictably chilly reception
text:
Citi Field gave Chase Utley a predictably chilly reception The Outside Corner 5 hrs ago TOC Locker © USA TODAY Sports Oct 12, 2015; New York City, NY, USA; Los Angeles Dodgers second baseman Chase Utley (26) before game three of the NLDS against the New York Mets at Citi Field. Mandatory Credit: Anthony Gruppuso-USA TODAY Sports During pregame introductions at Citi Field before Monday night’s NLDS Game 3, Mets fans gave Chase Utley an incredibly warm reception.
AdChoices Just kidding, they booed him like they’ve never booed anyone before.
The Citi Field reception for Chase Utley was not warm pic.twitter.com/EmCBhDyLYP
— Jake Kaplan (@jakemkaplan) October 13, 2015
Utley isn’t in the starting lineup for the Dodgers while he appeals his two-game suspension.
